WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:00:13.910 --> 00:00:15.700
All alone...

3
00:00:16.240 --> 00:00:19.930
<i>Sunday. A day off from torture.</i>

4
00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:35.630
Arm Power Up!!

5
00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:35.630
Too Easy to Win?!

6
00:00:31.840 --> 00:00:33.480
They have snacks!

7
00:00:33.480 --> 00:00:35.630
Oh, it's lured her in.

8
00:00:37.160 --> 00:00:39.530
In-chan, how's this machine look?

9
00:00:39.530 --> 00:00:41.230
Gimme a sec.

10
00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:47.880
Estimated cost: 300 yen.

11
00:00:47.880 --> 00:00:49.240
Closer look shows it's a new product.

12
00:00:49.240 --> 00:00:50.320
Slippery packaging.

13
00:00:50.550 --> 00:00:52.380
Pay-out ratio on the lower end.

14
00:00:52.380 --> 00:00:53.850
Looks like a money guzzler to me.

15
00:00:53.850 --> 00:00:55.540
Higher up in difficulty.

16
00:00:56.010 --> 00:00:59.170
Princess-chan, you should go 
for something else.

17
00:00:59.170 --> 00:01:00.950
Nope, this is the one.

18
00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:02.110
But it's...

19
00:01:02.440 --> 00:01:06.460
Since it's big enough 
to share if I win it!

20
00:01:06.460 --> 00:01:08.760
Princess-chan!

21
00:01:11.800 --> 00:01:13.430
Here goes nothing.

22
00:01:17.070 --> 00:01:20.230
Little more... Little more...

23
00:01:20.230 --> 00:01:22.400
Little more, little...

24
00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:23.600
Hey, stop!

25
00:01:33.210 --> 00:01:36.710
Not yet... Not yet...

26
00:01:37.450 --> 00:01:38.490
Not...

27
00:01:39.190 --> 00:01:40.310
Right there!

28
00:01:40.310 --> 00:01:41.580
Bam!

29
00:01:44.370 --> 00:01:45.500
Yes!

30
00:01:48.210 --> 00:01:51.490
That's good, that's good, that's...

31
00:01:51.490 --> 00:01:53.200
Ah!

32
00:01:53.630 --> 00:01:55.090
So sad...

33
00:01:55.090 --> 00:01:56.170
Let's try one more time!

34
00:01:56.170 --> 00:01:58.300
You were in the zone.

35
00:01:58.790 --> 00:02:00.440
All right...

36
00:02:01.660 --> 00:02:04.210
Oh yeah, where's Torture today?

37
00:02:04.210 --> 00:02:05.190
Ah.

38
00:02:05.190 --> 00:02:09.050
She said she was grabbing lunch 
with the new hire.

39
00:03:43.200 --> 00:03:44.990
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

40
00:03:49.870 --> 00:03:53.170
Rich Soy Sauce Ramen

41
00:03:50.370 --> 00:03:52.090
Come back soon!

42
00:03:53.160 --> 00:03:54.980
That was delicious.

43
00:03:54.980 --> 00:03:56.670
It was awesome.

44
00:03:56.670 --> 00:04:01.310
So you regularly check out restaurants 
as research for your torture?

45
00:04:01.310 --> 00:04:02.790
Now that's dedication, Senpai!

46
00:04:02.790 --> 00:04:04.640
Thanks, Sakura-chan.

47
00:04:05.360 --> 00:04:09.060
Oh yeah, who's the person 
you're currently torturing?

48
00:04:09.630 --> 00:04:11.930
That's classified information.

49
00:04:11.930 --> 00:04:13.890
Oh, I'm sorry.

50
00:04:13.890 --> 00:04:15.410
Don't worry about it.

51
00:04:15.410 --> 00:04:18.140
I'll tell you who it is once 
you're done with training.

52
00:04:18.140 --> 00:04:19.180
Yes!

53
00:04:19.530 --> 00:04:24.450
She often wanders around Hellholm, 
so you might catch a glimpse before then.

54
00:04:24.450 --> 00:04:26.780
You let a classified 
target just wander around?!

55
00:04:27.320 --> 00:04:31.650
I'd imagine you've heard of her.

56
00:04:31.650 --> 00:04:33.830
Huh, who could it be?

57
00:04:33.830 --> 00:04:37.080
I haven't heard about 
anyone being taken prisoner.

58
00:04:37.750 --> 00:04:41.610
I guess letting someone be captured by
the Hellhorde would harm your reputation.

59
00:04:41.610 --> 00:04:43.180
No wonder it's not public.

60
00:04:44.720 --> 00:04:48.420
I was hoping to try a few more places...

61
00:04:48.420 --> 00:04:51.570
But after ten stops, I'm far too full.

62
00:04:51.570 --> 00:04:52.630
Same here.

63
00:04:52.630 --> 00:04:55.600
I don't think I could enjoy 
eating any more than this.

64
00:04:56.350 --> 00:04:59.920
I haven't felt this full in ages.

65
00:05:00.380 --> 00:05:02.880
Happiness truly is a full stomach!

66
00:05:02.880 --> 00:05:04.320
Glad to hear it.

67
00:05:05.760 --> 00:05:08.110
Can't enjoy eating on a full stomach...

68
00:05:08.110 --> 00:05:10.870
Huh? That's right.

69
00:05:10.870 --> 00:05:14.120
They say hunger is the best spice.

70
00:05:15.220 --> 00:05:17.700
I've just come up with a great idea.

71
00:05:18.500 --> 00:05:20.880
The Next Day

72
00:05:19.030 --> 00:05:20.880
What?!

73
00:05:20.880 --> 00:05:24.130
Prisoner Mess Sergeants
Mr. & Mrs. Kobayashi

74
00:05:20.880 --> 00:05:24.130
You're going to have 
the princess go without breakfast?

75
00:05:24.130 --> 00:05:25.210
Yes.

76
00:05:25.210 --> 00:05:30.160
The idea is to leave her hungry to raise 
the odds of the torture succeeding.

77
00:05:30.160 --> 00:05:31.680
How cruel!

78
00:05:31.680 --> 00:05:33.380
Just look at her, Torture!

79
00:05:33.680 --> 00:05:39.110
She's so excited 
that it's almost breakfast time!

80
00:05:41.960 --> 00:05:44.850
All that waiting 
is making her drool a little!

81
00:05:46.390 --> 00:05:48.030
I-I shan't budge!

82
00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:52.200
At times, the plan calls 
for me to steel my heart.

83
00:05:52.200 --> 00:05:53.400
Ah!

84
00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:55.690
What is it, dear?

85
00:05:55.690 --> 00:05:57.400
Take a look at this!

86
00:05:57.400 --> 00:06:00.380
The princess looked so 
excited moments ago...

87
00:06:00.900 --> 00:06:05.220
And now she looks so sad 
since her breakfast is nowhere to be seen!

88
00:06:06.470 --> 00:06:08.090
She's looking all over!

89
00:06:08.090 --> 00:06:11.500
Her breakfast isn't coming, 
so she's in distress!

90
00:06:11.740 --> 00:06:12.710
So sad...

91
00:06:12.710 --> 00:06:14.550
She's down in the dumps!

92
00:06:15.100 --> 00:06:18.070
I can't bear to look!

93
00:06:18.460 --> 00:06:23.210
She's been reduced to writing
the hiragana for "no" on the ground!

94
00:06:18.970 --> 00:06:25.040
No... No... No...

95
00:06:19.480 --> 00:06:20.310
No

96
00:06:23.210 --> 00:06:25.580
She's a lost cause!

97
00:06:25.580 --> 00:06:27.420
I'm so sorry, Princess!

98
00:06:27.420 --> 00:06:30.560
We're powerless here...

99
00:06:40.910 --> 00:06:42.740
My apologies, Mr. and Mrs. Kobayashi!

100
00:06:42.740 --> 00:06:44.920
Please prepare some 
food for the princess!

101
00:06:46.260 --> 00:06:47.710
Can do!

102
00:06:47.710 --> 00:06:49.420
Wait for us, Princess!

103
00:06:49.420 --> 00:06:51.740
We'll have it out in a jiffy!

104
00:06:52.480 --> 00:06:57.440
<i>I was so worried about having the torture 
go well that I forgot something important.</i>

105
00:06:58.490 --> 00:07:01.520
<i>The most important thing 
for an inquisitor.</i>

106
00:07:01.520 --> 00:07:04.390
<i>Isn't the short-term gains...</i>

107
00:07:05.600 --> 00:07:07.500
Here you are, Princess!

108
00:07:07.500 --> 00:07:09.030
Sorry we're late!

109
00:07:12.370 --> 00:07:14.740
<i>But the smile on your 
torture target's face!</i>

110
00:07:16.280 --> 00:07:18.500
A sunny-side up egg and sausages!

111
00:07:18.820 --> 00:07:20.850
Good for you, Your Highness!

112
00:07:20.850 --> 00:07:22.540
Now that's a fine breakfast!

113
00:07:22.540 --> 00:07:24.370
Time to dig in!

114
00:07:35.940 --> 00:07:37.610
It's delicious!

115
00:07:37.940 --> 00:07:40.420
Today's seaweed is the 
seasoned kind, too!

116
00:07:40.420 --> 00:07:41.880
Awesome!

117
00:07:41.880 --> 00:07:45.240
Want to add some soy sauce 
and wrap your rice in it?

118
00:07:45.240 --> 00:07:46.390
Yeah!

119
00:07:51.900 --> 00:07:53.820
This is amazing!

120
00:07:54.150 --> 00:07:57.510
I was hungry, so it tastes even better!

121
00:07:55.670 --> 00:07:57.510
Mm-hmm.

122
00:07:59.370 --> 00:08:01.310
<i>'Tis exactly as you said.</i>

123
00:08:01.310 --> 00:08:05.310
<i>Hunger really is 
the best spice, Sakura-chan.</i>

124
00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:14.610
<i>Anyway, the princess confessed 
yet again during today's torture.</i>

125
00:08:15.900 --> 00:08:19.680
It seems the princess has 
a sister three years younger than her.

126
00:08:21.640 --> 00:08:23.430
What a coincidence.

127
00:08:23.430 --> 00:08:26.420
I'm three years younger 
than my brother as well.

128
00:08:27.530 --> 00:08:30.600
I feel a kinship with her now.

129
00:08:31.190 --> 00:08:35.200
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

130
00:08:31.190 --> 00:08:31.940
Roasted

131
00:08:31.190 --> 00:08:31.940
Seasoned

132
00:08:31.940 --> 00:08:32.690
Roasted

133
00:08:31.940 --> 00:08:32.690
Seasoned

134
00:08:32.690 --> 00:08:33.450
Roasted

135
00:08:32.690 --> 00:08:33.450
Seasoned

136
00:08:33.450 --> 00:08:33.700
Roasted

137
00:08:33.450 --> 00:08:33.700
Seasoned

138
00:08:33.700 --> 00:08:35.200
Roasted

139
00:08:33.700 --> 00:08:35.200
Seasoned

140
00:08:38.480 --> 00:08:39.650
Your Highness!

141
00:08:39.650 --> 00:08:40.780
Please resist!

142
00:08:40.780 --> 00:08:43.520
You mustn't let anyone see such 
an unbecoming face!

143
00:08:43.520 --> 00:08:44.880
How does this feel?

144
00:08:46.450 --> 00:08:47.630
Your Highness!

145
00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:49.880
Doesn't this feel good, too?

146
00:08:51.970 --> 00:08:54.220
Your Highness!

147
00:08:54.220 --> 00:08:58.130
<i>Why is the princess being 
subjected to such torture?</i>

148
00:08:58.980 --> 00:09:01.830
<i>It all began a little earlier.</i>

149
00:09:05.560 --> 00:09:08.390
My shoulders have been killing me lately.

150
00:09:08.390 --> 00:09:10.930
Oh, is everything okay?

151
00:09:10.930 --> 00:09:14.280
I was sure I was in good health, 
since I used to do physical training...

152
00:09:15.720 --> 00:09:16.870
Could it be?

153
00:09:19.580 --> 00:09:24.600
Have the days of grueling torture 
been eating away at my body?!

154
00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:29.390
It seems that we have 
very different definitions of "grueling."

155
00:09:29.830 --> 00:09:33.390
Little Princess, that 
could be from eyestrain.

156
00:09:33.390 --> 00:09:34.540
Eyestrain?

157
00:09:35.070 --> 00:09:37.510
My eyes? Even though it's 
my shoulders that hurt?

158
00:09:37.510 --> 00:09:41.120
When your eyes get tired, 
it leads to sore shoulders as well.

159
00:09:42.650 --> 00:09:43.720
I know.

160
00:09:44.070 --> 00:09:46.170
I'll give you a head spa treatment!

161
00:09:46.170 --> 00:09:47.860
Head spa?

162
00:09:50.640 --> 00:09:55.160
I'll begin by massaging 
the scalp as I wash your head.

163
00:09:57.180 --> 00:10:00.620
<i>A head spa sounded fancy, 
but she's shampooing my hair.</i>

164
00:10:00.620 --> 00:10:03.090
<i>I got this done all 
the time back at the castle—</i>

165
00:10:04.770 --> 00:10:05.880
Your Highness!

166
00:10:05.880 --> 00:10:07.320
What's the matter?!

167
00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:08.740
<i>What the heck?</i>

168
00:10:08.740 --> 00:10:10.830
<i>Man, this feels so good!</i>

169
00:10:11.080 --> 00:10:12.410
<i>If I had to compare it, yes!</i>

170
00:10:12.410 --> 00:10:14.210
<i>It feels just like... Just like...</i>

171
00:10:14.210 --> 00:10:17.810
<i>Like... Like... Like... Like?</i>

172
00:10:18.250 --> 00:10:21.220
<i>I give up! Can't think of anything!</i>

173
00:10:21.220 --> 00:10:23.430
Her Highness is making one 
hell of a comfy face!

174
00:10:23.430 --> 00:10:26.050
Feels sho goo...

175
00:10:26.050 --> 00:10:28.890
Let me rinse you off now.

176
00:10:28.890 --> 00:10:32.860
Comfy Face-o-Meter

177
00:10:30.320 --> 00:10:32.850
<i>The water's at just the 
right temperature.</i>

178
00:10:33.250 --> 00:10:38.500
<i>The word to describe this temperature 
isn't "warm" or "cold".</i>

179
00:10:38.500 --> 00:10:40.240
<i>It's "pleasant"!</i>

180
00:10:41.860 --> 00:10:44.740
Okay, let's massage the tightness away.

181
00:10:47.670 --> 00:10:48.970
<i>This is incredible!</i>

182
00:10:48.970 --> 00:10:51.820
<i>How can a head massage make me feel 
good down to the tips of my toes?!</i>

183
00:10:51.820 --> 00:10:53.710
<i>I can feel my blood flowing!</i>

184
00:10:53.710 --> 00:11:02.680
Fengchi

185
00:10:53.710 --> 00:10:56.180
This pressure point is called Fengchi.

186
00:10:56.180 --> 00:10:59.730
It's located on the back 
of your head around the hairline.

187
00:10:59.730 --> 00:11:02.680
It feels good to press it by yourself, 
so give it a shot sometime.

188
00:11:02.680 --> 00:11:05.810
Comfy Face-o-Meter

189
00:11:03.020 --> 00:11:05.020
Fengchi...

190
00:11:06.310 --> 00:11:08.680
I'm going to be massaging near your eyes.

191
00:11:08.680 --> 00:11:12.200
Jingming, effective 
for improving visual function.

192
00:11:12.190 --> 00:11:15.820
Comfy Face-o-Meter

193
00:11:12.200 --> 00:11:14.060
Jingming...

194
00:11:14.060 --> 00:11:15.830
Snap out of it, Your Highness!

195
00:11:15.830 --> 00:11:18.570
Yuyao, which can treat blurred vision.

196
00:11:18.570 --> 00:11:22.110
Comfy Face-o-Meter

197
00:11:18.570 --> 00:11:20.310
Yuyao!

198
00:11:20.310 --> 00:11:22.120
The comfy face train keeps going!

199
00:11:22.440 --> 00:11:25.020
Taiyang, good for headaches and vertigo.

200
00:11:25.020 --> 00:11:27.030
Taiyang!

201
00:11:25.030 --> 00:11:28.790
Comfy Face-o-Meter

202
00:11:27.030 --> 00:11:28.780
Your Highness!

203
00:11:29.100 --> 00:11:30.610
Does it feel good?

204
00:11:30.610 --> 00:11:32.840
Feelsh goo...

205
00:11:32.840 --> 00:11:35.290
There are other acupressure points.

206
00:11:35.290 --> 00:11:36.120
Please stop!

207
00:11:36.120 --> 00:11:39.610
Before her face turns too comfy 
to be fit to be seen!

208
00:11:39.610 --> 00:11:41.530
Go ahead!

209
00:11:41.530 --> 00:11:42.930
Your Highness!

210
00:11:42.930 --> 00:11:51.770
Comfy Face-o-Meter

211
00:11:42.930 --> 00:11:45.420
Yintang, which relieves nasal congestion.

212
00:11:45.420 --> 00:11:46.890
Yintang...

213
00:11:46.890 --> 00:11:49.550
Shanglianquan, which has 
a face-slimming effect.

214
00:11:49.550 --> 00:11:51.380
Shanglianquan...

215
00:11:51.760 --> 00:11:56.890
For stiff necks and shoulders, 
Xuanli, Shuaigu, Fubai.

216
00:11:56.890 --> 00:12:01.770
Xuanli, Shuaigu, Fubai...

217
00:11:56.900 --> 00:12:01.780
Comfy Face-o-Meter

218
00:12:02.070 --> 00:12:04.450
You can't show that face to the Legion!

219
00:12:06.080 --> 00:12:08.910
<i>My blood circulation's skyrocketing!</i>

220
00:12:08.910 --> 00:12:12.470
<i>All this pleasure is about to overflow!</i>

221
00:12:16.200 --> 00:12:19.170
<i>At this rate... At this rate...</i>

222
00:12:19.170 --> 00:12:21.460
<i>My pleasure dam's gonna burst!</i>

223
00:12:22.270 --> 00:12:24.240
Initiating emergency discharge!

224
00:12:26.610 --> 00:12:28.920
<i>Floodgates throughout 
my body are opening!</i>

225
00:12:28.920 --> 00:12:31.350
<i>The dam within me is releasing it all!</i>

226
00:12:31.830 --> 00:12:35.410
<i>It's more than just my head 
that's being massaged!</i>

227
00:12:36.150 --> 00:12:37.370
<i>It's my mind!</i>

228
00:12:37.370 --> 00:12:41.430
<i>My mind... My mind...</i>

229
00:12:48.850 --> 00:12:50.550
My body feels light!

230
00:12:50.550 --> 00:12:53.570
I feel like I could wipe out 
the Hellhorde empty-handed!

231
00:12:53.950 --> 00:12:56.430
Please don't.

232
00:12:56.810 --> 00:12:58.770
I'm filled with power!

233
00:13:00.360 --> 00:13:05.100
There's no way I'll cave 
to today's torture!

234
00:13:05.100 --> 00:13:09.000
I was worried there for a second, 
with how comfy you looked.

235
00:13:09.350 --> 00:13:11.360
But now the Hellhorde stands no chance!

236
00:13:11.360 --> 00:13:13.350
You can win, Your Highness!

237
00:13:14.120 --> 00:13:16.110
Oh, Princess-chan.

238
00:13:16.460 --> 00:13:18.300
You-chan! In-chan!

239
00:13:18.300 --> 00:13:21.010
Even more energetic than usual, I see.

240
00:13:21.010 --> 00:13:23.230
Yeah! I'm full of energy!

241
00:13:23.230 --> 00:13:26.490
Oh, did Giant give you 
a head spa treatment?

242
00:13:26.490 --> 00:13:27.860
She sure did!

243
00:13:27.860 --> 00:13:29.630
It feels good, doesn't it?

244
00:13:29.630 --> 00:13:31.170
It sure does!

245
00:13:31.170 --> 00:13:33.980
Princess, as for today's torture...

246
00:13:33.980 --> 00:13:35.450
Too bad!

247
00:13:35.450 --> 00:13:38.330
Her Highness has fully 
regained her power!

248
00:13:38.330 --> 00:13:40.830
Never again will she succumb 
to your torture—

249
00:13:40.000 --> 00:13:40.830
Hey, listen!

250
00:13:40.830 --> 00:13:42.010
You see, the king...

251
00:13:42.010 --> 00:13:44.010
Your Highness!

252
00:13:45.170 --> 00:13:48.260
The princess 
energetically confessed

253
00:13:49.440 --> 00:13:50.750
Your Majesty.

254
00:13:51.210 --> 00:13:54.000
It seems their king 
doesn't like sansho pepper.

255
00:13:55.030 --> 00:13:56.280
Oh?

256
00:13:58.330 --> 00:14:01.860
I find its unique flavor 
quite delectable.

257
00:14:02.570 --> 00:14:04.350
In fact, I love it so much...

258
00:14:05.030 --> 00:14:08.240
sometimes I find myself overdoing it.

259
00:14:10.010 --> 00:14:13.280
And what do you do when you add too much?

260
00:14:15.360 --> 00:14:16.980
What a foolish question.

261
00:14:16.980 --> 00:14:19.450
There's only one thing <i>to</i> do.

262
00:14:20.440 --> 00:14:22.090
Grin and bear it.

263
00:14:26.920 --> 00:14:28.970
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

264
00:14:29.880 --> 00:14:30.960
Princess!

265
00:14:32.070 --> 00:14:34.020
It's time for torture!

266
00:14:34.020 --> 00:14:35.510
'Kay!

267
00:14:35.960 --> 00:14:37.680
I know it's a bit late for this...

268
00:14:37.680 --> 00:14:39.730
but should you sound so enthusiastic 
about torture?

269
00:14:39.730 --> 00:14:41.780
Hold on a minute.

270
00:14:41.780 --> 00:14:43.230
'Kay!

271
00:14:44.400 --> 00:14:47.060
I'm sure Her Highness 
will fold again today...

272
00:14:48.450 --> 00:14:49.490
Ex.

273
00:14:50.380 --> 00:14:52.290
That look on Her Highness's face!

274
00:14:53.430 --> 00:14:55.990
She's finally managed to reclaim it!

275
00:14:56.690 --> 00:15:00.560
Her pride as Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion!

276
00:15:02.140 --> 00:15:03.080
Sorry.

277
00:15:03.280 --> 00:15:04.950
I was just imagining it!

278
00:15:05.530 --> 00:15:06.700
Sorry, Ex.

279
00:15:06.700 --> 00:15:09.130
You're completely ready to give in!

280
00:15:09.130 --> 00:15:11.340
Sorry. I mean it.

281
00:15:11.340 --> 00:15:13.820
At least go down with a fight!

282
00:15:11.890 --> 00:15:13.820
Um, lemme see...

283
00:15:13.820 --> 00:15:15.800
Sorry. Sorry. Sorry.

284
00:15:14.250 --> 00:15:15.800
Oh! Found it!

285
00:15:16.870 --> 00:15:20.430
Today's torture is a snack I really love!

286
00:15:20.430 --> 00:15:22.390
Oh? What is it?

287
00:15:22.390 --> 00:15:23.680
What do you think?

288
00:15:23.680 --> 00:15:25.850
Huh? What could it be?

289
00:15:25.850 --> 00:15:28.650
Something sweet? Or something salty?

290
00:15:28.650 --> 00:15:30.300
I see you're enjoying yourself.

291
00:15:30.300 --> 00:15:33.120
Hey, wanna see? Well?

292
00:15:33.120 --> 00:15:34.930
Yeah, I wanna see!

293
00:15:34.930 --> 00:15:37.030
I'll let you take a look then.

294
00:15:37.310 --> 00:15:38.600
Ta-da!

295
00:15:38.600 --> 00:15:41.040
Cream sandwich cookies!

296
00:15:41.370 --> 00:15:43.950
Oh, I like those as well!

297
00:15:43.950 --> 00:15:45.900
Really? That makes me happy!

298
00:15:45.900 --> 00:15:47.670
I'm happy, too!

299
00:15:47.950 --> 00:15:50.560
Oh, how surrenderable!

300
00:15:50.560 --> 00:15:52.700
What do you mean, "surrenderable"?!

301
00:15:52.700 --> 00:15:53.930
That's not even a real word!

302
00:15:55.600 --> 00:15:58.350
There's a special way 
we'll be eating these, too!

303
00:15:58.540 --> 00:15:59.410
What?

304
00:16:00.400 --> 00:16:04.310
You open up two cookies like this...

305
00:16:04.600 --> 00:16:07.930
and stack up the two pieces 
with cream filling.

306
00:16:09.020 --> 00:16:10.350
And there you have it!

307
00:16:10.350 --> 00:16:13.440
A special double cream cookie!

308
00:16:25.150 --> 00:16:26.330
<i>She got me!</i>

309
00:16:26.330 --> 00:16:28.700
<i>I was careless! Arrogant!</i>

310
00:16:29.440 --> 00:16:31.690
Today's torture is a slide!

311
00:16:31.690 --> 00:16:33.210
Yay!

312
00:16:34.060 --> 00:16:35.780
<i>Maomao-chan's torture...</i>

313
00:16:35.780 --> 00:16:39.730
<i>I was convinced it'd be 
a cute torture lacking bite like always.</i>

314
00:16:39.730 --> 00:16:42.810
<i>But two layers of cream filling?!</i>

315
00:16:42.810 --> 00:16:46.470
<i>I didn't expect such a 
perfectly hard-hitting torture!</i>

316
00:16:53.160 --> 00:16:55.700
<i>Just as I was caught 
completely off-guard...</i>

317
00:16:58.530 --> 00:17:00.410
<i>A crushing blow!</i>

318
00:17:08.170 --> 00:17:10.060
<i>My legs are trembling...</i>

319
00:17:10.060 --> 00:17:11.730
<i>They're about to buckle...</i>

320
00:17:12.220 --> 00:17:13.340
Your Highness?

321
00:17:13.340 --> 00:17:14.540
Are you okay?

322
00:17:15.310 --> 00:17:17.800
Ex, I can't go on.

323
00:17:17.800 --> 00:17:18.830
I'm...

324
00:17:18.830 --> 00:17:23.310
I have no idea why you've taken damage, 
but please bear it for now!

325
00:17:26.480 --> 00:17:28.090
<i>What's that sound?</i>

326
00:17:28.090 --> 00:17:29.680
<i>Some kind of pouring liquid?</i>

327
00:17:31.980 --> 00:17:36.770
Nothing goes better 
with cream-filled cookies than milk!

328
00:17:48.000 --> 00:17:49.250
Roar!

329
00:17:52.930 --> 00:17:53.980
Ah!

330
00:17:53.980 --> 00:17:57.000
Her Highness has yet again 
taken some form of damage!

331
00:17:59.380 --> 00:18:03.510
<i>The perfect torture 
unleashed by Maomao-chan.</i>

332
00:18:04.090 --> 00:18:08.120
<i>Was it Maomao-chan's 
growth bearing fruit?</i>

333
00:18:08.120 --> 00:18:12.410
<i>Or did she bring out a snack 
she liked by mere coincidence?</i>

334
00:18:12.410 --> 00:18:14.240
<i>That we cannot say.</i>

335
00:18:14.710 --> 00:18:20.060
<i>However, the result is that this torture 
forced the princess to surrender,</i>

336
00:18:20.060 --> 00:18:22.120
<i>more than any she had faced thus far.</i>

337
00:18:25.350 --> 00:18:29.400
<i>Upon total surrender, 
the words that came out of her mouth...</i>

338
00:18:31.530 --> 00:18:33.880
<i>were not secrets of the Royal Empire...</i>

339
00:18:36.930 --> 00:18:40.850
Thank you for being born into this world.

340
00:18:41.610 --> 00:18:44.780
<i>But words of gratitude for her life.</i>

341
00:18:46.490 --> 00:18:48.630
I don't believe it!

342
00:18:48.990 --> 00:18:50.260
Mao...

343
00:18:50.260 --> 00:18:52.990
Maomao-chan, you say?

344
00:18:52.990 --> 00:18:56.870
She inflicted such perfect torture...

345
00:19:01.120 --> 00:19:04.230
They sure do grow up fast.

346
00:19:05.120 --> 00:19:09.120
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

347
00:19:15.880 --> 00:19:17.880
Stop

348
00:19:15.880 --> 00:19:17.880
Snooze

349
00:19:23.380 --> 00:19:26.500
<i>7:30AM.</i>

350
00:19:23.390 --> 00:19:27.560
Stop

351
00:19:23.390 --> 00:19:27.560
Snooze

352
00:19:27.560 --> 00:19:29.280
<i>She gets out of bed.</i>

353
00:19:34.400 --> 00:19:35.590
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

354
00:19:35.590 --> 00:19:36.400
Your Highness!

355
00:19:36.400 --> 00:19:38.110
Please wake up! It's morning!

356
00:19:38.610 --> 00:19:40.200
Your Highness!

357
00:19:45.330 --> 00:19:46.070
Huh?

358
00:19:47.070 --> 00:19:49.770
Hey, I'm no alarm clock!

359
00:19:49.770 --> 00:19:51.390
Pressing there won't shut me up!

360
00:19:51.390 --> 00:19:53.080
Accept your fate and wake up!

361
00:19:53.080 --> 00:19:54.960
Ah, hey!

362
00:19:55.430 --> 00:20:00.820
<i>Normally, the princess would 
wake up now, but not today.</i>

363
00:19:59.190 --> 00:20:02.260
Beep, beep, beep!

364
00:20:02.260 --> 00:20:07.090
<i>She stayed up late last night playing 
video games with Youki and Inki.</i>

365
00:20:10.040 --> 00:20:11.100
I win!

366
00:20:11.100 --> 00:20:12.960
One more! One more match!

367
00:20:11.400 --> 00:20:14.270
Your Highness, it's 
about time you went to sleep.

368
00:20:12.960 --> 00:20:14.700
Pretty please, In-chan!

369
00:20:14.700 --> 00:20:16.310
Sure, I'm down.

370
00:20:16.310 --> 00:20:19.610
All of you! It's eleven o'clock!

371
00:20:16.310 --> 00:20:18.630
Maybe I should try a new character.

372
00:20:18.630 --> 00:20:20.400
Oh, can I pick the stage?

373
00:20:20.660 --> 00:20:21.620
Fine by me.

374
00:20:21.620 --> 00:20:23.620
Hey, are you listening?!

375
00:20:23.960 --> 00:20:25.130
Your Highness?!

376
00:20:25.130 --> 00:20:27.060
Ah, she got me again!

377
00:20:27.450 --> 00:20:31.000
<i>As a result, she's not waking up today.</i>

378
00:20:31.000 --> 00:20:33.200
Your Highness! Good morning!

379
00:20:37.610 --> 00:20:39.450
<i>7:45.</i>

380
00:20:39.450 --> 00:20:41.350
<i>She puts the futon away...</i>

381
00:20:43.980 --> 00:20:45.770
<i>and begins washing her face.</i>

382
00:20:46.820 --> 00:20:50.280
<i>However, the princess 
hasn't left her bed today.</i>

383
00:20:50.280 --> 00:20:52.350
Your Highness! Bonjour!

384
00:20:53.190 --> 00:20:54.370
<i>8:00.</i>

385
00:20:54.720 --> 00:20:56.360
<i>Stretches.</i>

386
00:20:57.670 --> 00:21:02.550
<i>They improve circulation and serve as 
a way to check for any bodily symptoms,</i>

387
00:21:02.550 --> 00:21:04.980
<i>or at least they would normally...</i>

388
00:21:05.600 --> 00:21:08.880
<i>However, the princess 
hasn't left her bed today.</i>

389
00:21:08.880 --> 00:21:10.870
Your Highness! Guten Morgen!

390
00:21:11.550 --> 00:21:14.870
<i>No, the truth is she doesn't 
normally do any of this.</i>

391
00:21:15.160 --> 00:21:20.950
<i>Everyday, she thinks to herself, 
"I should do this!" but does not.</i>

392
00:21:20.950 --> 00:21:24.890
<i>She spends this time lazing in bed 
and looking at her phone.</i>

393
00:21:24.890 --> 00:21:28.300
<i>8:30. Breakfast.</i>

394
00:21:28.300 --> 00:21:30.900
Princess, it's time to eat.

395
00:21:30.900 --> 00:21:32.860
Yay...

396
00:21:32.860 --> 00:21:34.600
<i>She always wakes up.</i>

397
00:21:34.600 --> 00:21:37.340
Go on and wash your face first.

398
00:21:37.340 --> 00:21:38.520
Yeah...

399
00:21:39.210 --> 00:21:43.850
<i>No matter how late she goes to bed, 
she always wakes up for this.</i>

400
00:21:46.110 --> 00:21:48.110
Busy, busy...

401
00:21:54.830 --> 00:21:57.000
Time to dig in!

402
00:22:04.010 --> 00:22:05.580
It's delicious!

403
00:22:05.960 --> 00:22:08.770
<i>Breakfast at 8:30.</i>

404
00:22:06.500 --> 00:22:11.500
